description:
Stephen D. Lewis brings a word of comfort to the family and friends of Bishop Eddie Long during this time of sadness and reminds us that this is not a time of judgement but of personal reflection and hope for the day of resurrection will reveal all.

Lesson 9: http://thepresenttruth.org/resources/bible-school/approved-watchman/lesson-09-what-happens-when-people-die/

Subscribe to The Present Truth Channel: https://goo.gl/EU2jOf

////////////////

www.thepresenttruth.org

“Specialties” is where Stephen D. Lewis pays tribute to those who have recently lost of a loved one.

ABOUT THE SPEAKER
Stephen D. Lewis is a man who understands what it means to be saved by grace. That understanding is clearly seen in his passion for Christ and his love for people. 

Lewis is the featured speaker of the television and radio program, The Present Truth, which is nationally broadcast on several stations. His interest and aim is on winning and reviving personal commitments to a Saviour, Jesus, the Christ, "so that we can go home!”
